ent-CMWeaponPistolM1984Custom-name = Custom M1984 service pistol
ent-CMWeaponPistolM1984Custom-desc = A M1984 Service Pistol, once the standard issue sidearm of the Marines but has recently been replaced with the M77 combat pistol. Fires 9mm pistol rounds. This one has had it's wooden grips replaced with gaudy ivory ones.
